ll.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60c80d5f065875de44caf65187e27839e3862d0","tid":2494047,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4920157dc3ec4b81453e05fe65407fa804d841a4","tid":2494047,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c34e7813d5905a1dd6a23fd6af4168d0a449826","tid":2494047,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"80af4623c73fc7c631754d56f5dacfa68dd22f7c","tid":2494047,"uid":183214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0b0768d6298ed3f94f30c447a791af35322602c","tid":2494047,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:12:29.000Z","msg":"重光團隊:<br />\n<br />\n【倫敦戶外香港廣告最後今日！然後轉戰網上！】<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位香港人同傳媒，喺過去一星期對重光團隊喺倫敦推出嘅香港民族身份廣告，作出廣泛報道同支持 ( 仲要多謝埋黨報加持！ ) 。<br />\n<br />\n今日係戶外廣告牌嘅最後一日，如果身處英國又想親身去睇吓嘅朋友，就要把握最後機會啦！聽日開始就會轉戰網上攻勢，接觸更多唔同地區層面嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n🚖 出發前記住留意廣告播放時間：<br />\nSun 18th April | 🕚11:00-🕛12:00 ｜🕟16:00-🕠17:00 ｜ 🕣20:00-🕤21:00<br />\n<br />\n我哋好慶幸今次嘅行動能夠引起社會嘅迴響同討論，亦收到好多世界各地互相支持同鼓勵嘅訊息，我哋亦會審慎聆聽各種唔同嘅建議。<br />\n<br />\n自2019年6月起，身處世界各地嘅我哋，受到香港手足前仆後繼嘅無畏精神感召，故而聚集埋一齊，組成今日嘅團隊，為香港付出。我地團隊內部一直秉持各施其職、無大台、無大佬嘅精神，盡量做到每位成員都有話語權。而籌得嘅款項亦存放喺一個有文明法律保障嘅地方，代價之一係我哋團隊使用資金嘅時候，要按眾籌時所訂下嘅目標承諾如實運用，實報實銷。箇中詳情，我哋會喺唔危及到手足安全嘅情況下保持透明度，並期待重光之後可以一一詳盡公開。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，相信香港人同團隊一樣都無遺忘一眾手足，希望睇到呢度嘅你妳你妳都可以幫幫612手捐款，支持有需要嘅手足 ➡️ <a href=\"http://donate.612fund.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdonate.612fund.hk&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=37664341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">donate.612fund.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n如果去咗英國嘅手足有需要、或者想幫手嘅話，記得去 <a href=\"http://UKxHK.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FUKxHK.info&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=284c6919\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">UKxHK.info</a> 嗰網站睇吓。<br />\n<br />\n最後要講嘅係，希望今次嘅廣告可以為香港人稍作打氣，同埋比本地英國人知道點解陸續有香港人選擇投奔英國建立新嘅家園，期望兩個族群能夠漸漸地互相交流、理解、共融，並且得以連結。<br />\n<br />\n「黎明前係最黑暗嘅，<br />\n但亦係最接近光明嘅時候！」<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#齊上齊落<br />\n#StandwithHongKong #ThankYouUK #UKxHK<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n重光團隊 SWHK Channel 🏴<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/FFFSWHK20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFFFSWHK20&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpkzY%2BUnkXQH0zW%2FJu7eEK44%3D&h=9eab0416\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/FFFSWHK20</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:20:14.000Z","msg":"push, PR no way<br />\n手置 plz"},{"pid":"9e79ff3e251805166b016a1df8b153f55d5b78eb","tid":2494047,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9239242dd8327fcb9e50bd4cf1ed52ded73bda86","tid":2494047,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl